                            U. S. District Court

                              District of Maine

                   E-Mail Notification Service "usdcnews"

   All attorneys and members of the public are now able to receive e-mail
   messages from the U.S. District Court notifying them whenever a new
   opinion or a revision to the local rules has been posted to the court's
   web site (http://www.med.uscourts.gov). The Clerk's Office will also
   use the e-mail service to inform counsel of news of general interest.
   To join, click on the link below and then select "join".

   go to usdcnews page
